<P>
New San Francisco Opera Music Director: Scottish conductor Donald Runnicles has 
been appointed San Francisco Opera music director effective January, 1992. 
Runnicles, Generalmusikdirektor of the Stadtische Buhnen in Freiburg, Germany, 
is the second person to hold the post after the death of Sir John Pritchard 
last December. Sir Charles Mackerras has been named principal guest conductor 
beginning in 1993. CLAUDIA PUIG 
