<HEADLINE>
<P>
HIGH SCHOOL ROUNDUP; 
</P>
<P>
THOUSAND OAKS, SCHERREI DEFEAT SIMI VALLEY IN WATER POLO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Chuck Scherrei scored four goals to lead Thousand Oaks High to a 10-5 victory 
over Simi Valley in a Marmonte League water polo match at Thousand Oaks on 
Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
Bob Martinich added three goals and three assists for Thousand Oaks (8-6, 3-0 
in league play). 
</P>
<P>
Thousand Oaks will play Royal (12-3, 3-0) in a battle for first place Thursday 
at Royal. 
</P>
<P>
In other water polo matches: 
</P>
