<TEXT>
<P>
Great Western Completes Deal: The Beverly Hills thrift assumes $745 million in 
deposits and 13 branches in Florida formerly owned by Carteret Savings Bank of 
Morristown, N.J. Great Western, which has been expanding rapidly in Florida by 
buying thrift operations, paid a premium of $28.2 million. 
</P>
