<HEADLINE>
<P>
FISHING REPORT: PLENTY OF BASS AWAIT PUDDINGSTONE ANGLERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Southland bass fishermen have been finding their quarry to be more than 
cooperative at Puddingstone Reservoir. 
</P>
<P>
Butch Ham of Chino spent one day catching -- and releasing -- 52 bass weighing 
up to six pounds. 
</P>
<P>
"And I got a call yesterday from a guy who caught 45," lake spokesman Ron 
Lindbloom said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
